    "description": "轰隆！城堡随着巨响崩毁，公主被恶魔掳走。作为王国最强大的剑士，守护国家安宁，救回公主是你义不容辞地责任。踏上征程前，你永远无法想象前方有多少敌人和险关，只能相信手中的长剑，斩荆棘，赴魔窟，无所畏惧地前进！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117930/extras/5f97ec38f8db44c36571f6e1484f0068.avif?t=1641537524\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br>《惊奇剑士》作为一款横版2D动作闯关冒险游戏，通过可爱逗趣的漫画美术风格，描绘出一个个独具特色，让人捧腹的NPC和怪物，满足了每个玩家孩童时幻想的、光怪陆离的冒险世界。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117930/extras/099ba42cc71338fa93e7e582ea0e3b58.avif?t=1641537524\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br>畅爽的战斗动作，搭配火焰、冰冻、雷电三种属性不同的魔法，组合成多样华丽的连击技能，不断利用终结技、闪避等技巧挑战反应极限，一定会给热衷于硬核格斗玩家带来最纯正的战斗体验，达成自己的专属成就。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117930/extras/a4fdb821a67f5d7f5f26c329be346241.avif?t=1641537524\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117930/extras/f794d037c9a1a20a3770c59176807464.avif?t=1641537524\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br>游戏中也融入了经典的RPG元素，每次冒险之后，获得的经验可用来增强属性和技能，收集不同的装备和道具都能让你的剑士变得更强。同时还可以挑选搞怪有趣的套装，恶搞经典角色，在紧张刺激的冒险中也能体会到成长自定义的乐趣。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117930/extras/5d40383ac49357190aa0c7c0011d0d5e.avif?t=1641537524\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117930/extras/467efd50eca01b58c3592195e631408d.avif?t=1641537524\" width=500 height=240 /></span><br>你会在森林中驱赶马车躲避盗贼的炸弹，也能在机械城驾驶高达发射激光，还有雪山滑雪、海底捕鱼等横版射击、跑酷的玩法，让你的旅途不只有打打杀杀，充满了纯正的街机味道。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117930/extras/5f1437793730a1a66af32db3aa600e11.avif?t=1641537524\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117930/extras/ef551c47eb303eff9024f4e9b889c69a.avif?t=1641537524\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117930/extras/347d58526500fe75d95c8f7578a85b03.avif?t=1641537524\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br>近期游戏更新了全新的宠物系统，挑选自己的旅行伙伴，也会带来独特属性，从此旅途不再孤单。在装备、道具、套装、技能等方面未来还会不断扩充崭新的内容，拓展更加广阔的冒险区域，解锁全新成就。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1117930/extras/c89ace05b778d43f3bc07c8c6ea509eb.avif?t=1641537524\" width=500 height=242 /></span>",
